# To generate the HAR file for Google Chrome

1. Open Google Chrome & go to the problem page.
2. Press Ctrl + Shift + I OR From menu bar select View > Developer > Developer Tools.
3. From Opened panel, select the Network tab.
4. Look for a round Record button ( Record button ) in the upper left corner of the Network tab, and make sure it is red.If it is grey, click it once to start recording.
5. Select Preserve log .
6. Click "Clear button" to clear out any existing logs from the Network tab.
7. Reproduce the issue that you were experiencing before, while the network requests are being recorded.
8. Once you have reproduced the issue, right click anywhere on the grid of network requests, select Save as HAR with Content , and save it to computer.
